BRELOOM closes in on its foe with light
and sprightly footwork, then throws
punches with its stretchy arms. This POKMONs fighting technique puts
boxers to shame.

The seeds ringing BRELOOMs tail are
made of hardened toxic spores. It is
horrible to eat the seeds. Just taking a bite of this POKMONs
seed will cause your stomach to rumble.

It scatters spores from holes in the cap

climates. It feeds on trees and plants in
fields and forests.

Chapignon se rapproche de son ennemi en se servant de

est digne des meilleurs boxeurs.

Die Kampftechnik dieses Pokmon treibt Profiboxern die
Schamesrte ins Gesicht.

Breloom se acerca al enemigo realizando un juego de piernas

dejan en ridculo al boxeador ms profesional.

Breloom si avvicina al nemico con passettini leggeri e veloci,

Le sue tecniche di lotta superano quelle dei pugili pi esperti.

Las semillas que Breloom tiene prendidas de la cola estn
